    public interface Draggable
    An interface provided by objects that can be dragged. The DragContext provided in the drag(DragContext) method includes information on the screen coordinates and the state of the WorldWindow.

    • Method Summary

      Modifier and Type Method Description
      void drag​(DragContext dragContext)
      Drag the object given the provided DragContext.
      boolean isDragEnabled()
      Indicates whether the object is enabled for dragging.
      void setDragEnabled​(boolean enabled)
      Controls whether the object is enabled for dragging.
